cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.CY 

This paper involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques for mining social media messages, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also involves information retrieval (IR) techniques for identifying relevant tweets, which is another sub-category of CS. The use of neural networks for classification falls under the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves social media analysis (cs.SI) and cybernetics (cs.CY) as it deals with analyzing social media messages and developing automated classification models.
